summary: This new code file, moviepage9.html, introduces a webpage for displaying information about a specific movie, "Captain America Civil War." It includes the movie title, poster image, summary, and an embedded YouTube video trailer. Additionally, it allows users to provide a rating for the movie using a star rating system and submit it to the server. The file also includes a menu bar for navigation to other pages in the system. The file contributes to the overall system by providing a platform for displaying movie details and gathering user feedback through ratings.
